<lb ed="L" n="0282b12"/><cb:div type="note"><entry><form>黽</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0282b1202" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">弭盡切音泯勉也刀所不堪心所不欲而勉強為之曰黽</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>締</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0282b1225" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">特計切音弟結
